'''''Radley''''' was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] which carried [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing]] prototypes and delivered them to the ''[[Cathleen]]''.

While a [[Blue Squadron (Rebel Alliance)/Legends|Blue Squadron]] [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|A-wing]] guarded it, its [[Deflector shield/Legends|shield]] system malfunctioned and had to be relieved by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]]. During that time, the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|Nebulon-B frigate]] [[Interceptor (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Interceptor'']] approached and launched [[TIE series/Legends|TIEs]] that attempted to destroy the freighter.

Farlander was able to ward them back until the ''Cathleen'' came and received the cargo.

